/** ****************************************************************************
 * Name        : NAS_CTTF_HRPD_SNP_DATA_CANCEL_REQ_STRU
 *
 * Description : This signal is used as cancel request from NAS to SNP, then
 * SNP tries to cancel this related air-message sent by NAS before. There is no
 * response about cancel-req signal, even fail to cancel the data-req. If
 * cancel successfully, and the canceled message needs confirm, SNP will reply
 * fail to NAS by SNP-DATA-CNF; if the canceled message does not need confirm,
 * SNP will not reply SNP-DATA-CNF.
 *
 * ATTENTION:
 * If this message has been transmitted or being transmitting, it can not
 * cancel it any more. Message has not been transmitted at all, it can be
 * canceled.
 *******************************************************************************/
